        "name": "Preternatural Polish",
        "type": "stat_block_section",
        "subtype": "feat",
        "text": "Armor you polish shines with righteous grace. You can take 10 minutes to recite prayers or oaths while polishing a suit of heavy armor that you or a willing creature is wearing. If you do, attempt a DC 35 Crafting check with the following results. The armor then becomes temporarily immune to this ability until your next daily preparations.",
